{
  "id": "adv_event_2410_01_01",
  "title": "あの日\n交わした約束",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "前の仕事が予定より長引いたわね\n早く次の現場に移動しないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The previous job ran longer than scheduled.\nI need to hurry to the next location…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 7.1368027688,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6666.6666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.34170084
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ？　琴乃ちゃん？\nわぁぁぁ！！　やっぱり琴乃ちゃんだ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? Kotono-chan?\nWaaah!! It really is Kotono-chan!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.34170084,
      "endTime": 14.4085260391,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.6083675067
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、さくら！？　ちょ、ちょっと\nこんな人通りの多い所で、声が大きいって！　静かに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ Sakura!? W-wait‚\nyour voice is too loud in such a crowded place! Keep it down!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.6083675067,
      "endTime": 22.206508032499997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.4114061038
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ごめん……\n琴乃ちゃんに会えたのが嬉しくて、つい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ sorry…\nI was so happy to see you‚ I couldn't help myself…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.4114061038,
      "endTime": 28.7064174335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.9114061038
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "全く……\nふふっ……でもこんな所で会うなんて奇遇ね、さくら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really…\nFufu… but seeing you in a place like this is quite a coincidence‚ Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.9114061038,
      "endTime": 35.8885487239,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.0934467952
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね～。私は撮影の帰りだけど\n琴乃ちゃんはこれからお仕事？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right~ I'm on my way back from shooting.\nAre you heading to work‚ Kotono-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.0934467952,
      "endTime": 42.948752752999994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.1601134618
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、さっきまでテレビの収録をしていて\nこの後は雑誌のインタビューとライブのリハーサルよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I was recording for TV until just now‚\nand after this I have a magazine interview and live rehearsal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.1601134618,
      "endTime": 50.6566666921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.8615647634
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4になってから月ストも大忙しだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moon Tempest has been really busy since becoming BIG4.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.8615647634,
      "endTime": 54.9275965055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.1282314301
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "最近は月ストのみんなと全然話せてないから\n琴乃ちゃんと久しぶりにお喋り出来て嬉しいよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I haven't been able to talk with everyone from Moon Tempest lately‚\nso I'm happy to chat with you after so long‚ Kotono-chan~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.1282314301,
      "endTime": 62.6458050728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.8615647634
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。お互いに時間が取れなくて\n里帰りライブもいつになったら出来るのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. We both can't find time‚\nso when will we be able to do the homecoming live…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.8615647634,
      "endTime": 69.4589795431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.6638776144
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "里帰りライブかぁ……\nみんなで海を見ながら約束したよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Homecoming live…\nWe all promised while looking at the sea‚ didn't we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.6638776144,
      "endTime": 76.2775058111,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8000
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "目標……じゃないかもしれないんだけど\n月ストとやりたいことはあるよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It might not be a goal… but there is something\nwe want to do with Moon Tempest!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.4638776144,
      "endTime": 85.6282327017,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "私達とやりたいこと……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Something you want to do with us…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.7997979483,
      "endTime": 88.594899877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　今一番私達サニピがやりたいことはね……\n月ストと一緒に星見市で里帰りライブがしたいの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah! What we Sunny Peace want to do most right now is…\nwe want to do a homecoming live in Hoshimi City together with Moon Tempest!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.7997979483,
      "endTime": 98.8388230643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.9997979483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "月ストとサニピの合同里帰りライブ……\n早く実現しないかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moon Tempest and Sunny Peace's joint homecoming live…\nI wish it would happen soon…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.0331312817,
      "endTime": 107.9258298558,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.1331312817
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　今から二人でお茶しない？\nどんな合同ライブにするか打ち合わせしようよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's it! How about having tea together now?\nLet's plan what kind of joint live we should do!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.1331312817,
      "endTime": 115.6812720936,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.866464615
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "とても楽しそうな提案だけど……ごめんなさい\nすぐに次の現場に行かなきゃいけなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's a very fun proposal‚ but… I'm sorry.\nI have to go to the next location right away…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.866464615,
      "endTime": 123.0084829332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.2133855822
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "あ……そうだよね……\nごめん！　合同ライブのお話はまた今度しよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… that's right…\nSorry! Let's talk about the joint live another time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.2133855822,
      "endTime": 130.3676941874,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12353.281084499997
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.5800522489
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、楽しみにしてるわ\nそれじゃ、またね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right‚ I'm looking forward to it.\nWell then‚ see you later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.5800522489,
      "endTime": 135.37558523840002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.813820712
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "いってらっしゃーい！　お仕事頑張ってね～！\nはぁ……「また今度」って、いつになるんだろう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Take care! Good luck with work~!\nSigh… \"another time\"… when will that be…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.813820712,
      "endTime": 148.3349320097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.6846598946
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その日の夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――That night",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.3471540453,
      "endTime": 150.52714796089998,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_write-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8919.512621400003
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "う～ん、やっぱりここはこの曲かな？\nでも、こっちの曲もいいよね……",
