      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_01-skr027.m4a",
      "text": "スケジュールの調整とか難しいのは分かりますけど\n早くやらせて下さい！　みんなムズムズしてるんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand that schedule coordination is difficult‚ but\nplease let us do it soon! Everyone's getting restless!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 425.7446506662,
      "endTime": 434.0701605005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
